Emy Coligado https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emy_Coligado 0 Emy Coligado (born June 5, 1971 in Geneva, Ohio) is an American actress, known for her role as Piama Tananahaakna on the sitcom Malcolm in the Middle. In 2001, Coligado landed a recurring role as Emmy, the medical examiner's assistant, on the drama Crossing Jordan. Coligado also appears on NBC's web series CTRL as well as Poppy Tang in NBC's Chuck. She also played Ling in The Three Stooges. Emy_Coligado ( born June_5 , 1971 in Geneva , Ohio ) is an_American_actress , known for her_role as Piama_Tananahaakna on the_sitcom_Malcolm in the_Middle .
